1 Active candidates

mss %<>% mutate(name = paste(first_name, last_name, sep = ' ')) #%>% select(-first_name, -last_name)
active.candidates <- mss %>% filter(active == "Yes")%$% name


disp.can <- function(NAME){
  mss%>% filter(name==NAME)  %>% 
  select(active:reasons_final_outcome,cmt_mem1, cmt_mem2, g1q0:g1q2,what_do_you_see_as_your_gr:what_topics_do_you_think_t___11  ) %>% 
    remove.blank.columns() %>% t() %>% as.data.frame() %>% rownames_to_column(., "variable") %>% 
    left_join(., mss.labels, by = "variable") %>%
    left_join(., mss.dict %>% select(-label), by = "variable") %>%
    select(form, Item = label, Value = V1)  %>% 
    fill(., "form", .direction = "down") %>%
    gt(groupname_col = "form") %>% 
      opt_row_striping() %>%
      gt::tab_options(table_body.hlines.color = "white",
                      row.striping.background_color = "#fafafa",
                      source_notes.font.size = 12,
                      table.font.size = 12,
                      heading.align = "left",
                      heading.title.font.size = 16,
                      table.border.top.color = "transparent",
                      table.border.top.width = px(3),
                      data_row.padding = px(4)) %>%
      gt::tab_header(NAME) }


candidate.list <- lapply(active.candidates, disp.can)

2 Staff interview record

path <- "/Users/joshvumc/OneDrive - VUMC/MS staff hiring committee - General/Interview record.xlsx"
staff <- readxl::read_excel(path, sheet = "staff")%>% filter(on.staff == "staff") %>% 
  select(Name, committee, start.date)%>% mutate(start.date = ymd(start.date))
int.record <- bind_rows(readxl::read_excel(path, sheet = "int.record"),
                       readxl::read_excel(path, sheet = "current")) %>% mutate(date = ymd(date))

2.1 Phone screen

int.record%>% filter(date > (today()-years(1)), type == "Phone screen", Name %in% staff$Name ) %>%
  group_by(Name) %>% mutate(n = n(), days.since = as.numeric(today()-date)) %>% 
  left_join( staff %>% select(Name),. , by = "Name") %>%
  mutate(n = replace_na(n, 0)) %>%
  bind_rows(., staff %>% filter(start.date > (today()-years(1))) %>% select(-committee)) %>%
  group_by(Name) %>% fill(., n, .direction ="updown") %>%
  mutate(total.days.since = sum(days.since)) %>%
  arrange(days.since, total.days.since, n, start.date, Name) %>%
  ungroup() %>% mutate(Name = fct_inorder(Name)) %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x = date, y = Name)) + geom_point() + 
  geom_point(aes(x = start.date), colour = "red") +
  facet_grid(n~., scales = "free_y", space = "free")

2.2 Reference check

int.record%>% filter(date > (today()-years(1)), type %in% c("Reference check", "Committee interview"), Name %in% staff$Name ) %>%
  group_by(Name) %>% mutate(n = n(), days.since = as.numeric(today()-max(date))) %>% 
  left_join( staff%>% filter(committee == "yes") %>% select(Name),. , by = "Name") %>%
  mutate(n = replace_na(n, 0)) %>%
  arrange(days.since, n, Name) %>%
  ungroup() %>% mutate(Name = fct_inorder(Name)) %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x = date, y = Name, colour = type)) + geom_point() + facet_grid(n~., scales = "free_y", space = "free")

2.3 On-site/ Zoom interviews

int.record%>% filter(date > (today()-years(1)), type %in% c("Interview", "Committee interview"), Name %in% staff$Name ) %>%

PH <- phone %>% select(-Total) %>% pivot_longer(., -Member) %>% filter(value != "", Member != "") %>% 
  mutate(type = ifelse(grepl("ref|Ref", value), "Reference check", "Phone screen")) %>%
  mutate(value = str_trim(gsub("Ref-|ref-|Ref -", "", value), "both")) %>% arrange(value)%>% 
  mutate(name = gsub("\\.1$", "", name)) %>%
  mutate(name = gsub("X", "", name), date = mdy(name)) %>% arrange(date) %>%
  select(Member, date, candidate = value, type) #%>%group_by(Member, type) %>% tally() %>% arrange(type, n)

3 All candidate summary

## Read files in to look at resumes over time

resumes <- data.frame(file = list.files("../../applications/active applications",  
                                        pattern="*.pdf", full.names=FALSE)) %>%
  mutate(file = gsub(".pdf", "", file))%>% 
  separate(., file, into = c("date", "name"), sep = 10) %>% mutate(date = ymd(date)) %>% 
  mutate(position = case_when(grepl("B3|III", name) ~ "B3", grepl("B1", name) ~ "B1", TRUE ~ "B2" )) %>%
  mutate(name = str_trim(gsub("\\(B3\\)", "", name), "both")) %>%
  mutate(name = str_trim(gsub("\\(B1\\)", "", name), "both")) %>%
  mutate(status = "current")

inactive <- data.frame(file = list.files("../../applications/inactive applications",  
                                        pattern="*.pdf", full.names=FALSE)) %>%
  mutate(file = gsub(".pdf", "", file))%>% separate(., file, into = c("date", "name"), sep = 10) %>% 
  mutate(date = ymd(date)) %>% mutate(position = case_when(grepl("B3|III", name) ~ "B3",
                                                           grepl("B1", name) ~ "B1",
                                                           TRUE ~ "B2" )) %>%
  mutate(name = str_trim(gsub("\\(B3\\)", "", name), "both")) %>%
  mutate(name = str_trim(gsub("\\(B1\\)", "", name), "both")) %>%
  mutate(status = "inactive")

processing <- data.frame(file = list.files("../../applications/processing",  
                                        pattern="*.pdf", full.names=FALSE)) %>%
  mutate(file = gsub(".pdf", "", file))%>% separate(., file, into = c("date", "name"), sep = 10) %>% 
  mutate(date = ymd(date)) %>% mutate(position = case_when(grepl("B3|III", name) ~ "B3",
                                                           grepl("B1", name) ~ "B1",
                                                           TRUE ~ "B2" )) %>%
  mutate(name = str_trim(gsub("\\(B3\\)", "", name), "both")) %>%
  mutate(name = str_trim(gsub("\\(B1\\)", "", name), "both")) %>%
  mutate(status = "processing")

candidate.resumes <- bind_rows(resumes, inactive, processing)



candidate.summary <- mss %>% select(1, contains("name"), active_reason) %>% mutate(name = paste(first_name, last_name)) %>%
  dplyr::slice(279:nrow(.)) %>%
  fuzzyjoin::stringdist_join(.,candidate.resumes , 
                by='name', #match based on team
                mode='left', #use left join
                method = "jw", #use jw distance metric
                max_dist=99, 
                distance_col='dist') %>%
  group_by(name.x) %>%
  slice_min(order_by=dist, n=1)  %>% arrange(study_id) %>%
  rename(redcap_name = name.x, name = name.y) %>%
  left_join(candidate.resumes, ., by = c("name", "date", "position", "status")) %>%
  select(name, redcap_name, date, position, status, study_id, active_reason) %>%
  arrange(desc(date), status, study_id)
